ts%20of%20four%20people%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20Armenia%2C%20the%20dismantling%20of%20more%20than%20100%20malicious%20computer%20servers%20worldwide%2C%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%20over%202%2C000%20domains%2C%20according%20law%20enforcement%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20suspects%20raked%20in%20at%20least%20%2470%20million%20in%20cryptocurrency%20by%20%26quot%3Brenting%20out%20criminal%20infrastructure%20sites%20to%20deploy%20ransomware%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europol.europa.eu%2Fmedia-press%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2Flargest-ever-operation-against-botnets-hits-dropper-malware-ecosystem%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Europol%2C%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agency%20of%20the%20European%20Union%20that%20conducted%20the%20operation%20along%20with%20other%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECybersecurity%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20takedown%20is%20a%20pivotal%20step%20forward%20in%20the%20ongoing%20war%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fransomware-attacks-corporations-children-executives-mandiant-google-cyber-security-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybercrime%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20they%20said%2C%20the%20fight%20can't%20end%20here%2C%20as%20cybercrime%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20threats%20facing%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20this%20is%20going%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20great%20step%20in%20addressing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adam%20Wandt%2C%20a%20cybercrime%20investigations%20expert%20and%20a%20public%20policy%20professor%20at%20New%20York's%20John%20Jay%20College%20of%20Criminal%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c59c7ca2-3119-4ab7-986e-f21258b45fe3%5C%22%3E'Largest%20ever%20operation%20against%20botnets'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEuropol%20called%20the%20sting%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20ever%20operation%20against%20botnets%2C%20which%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20deployment%20of%20ransomware.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Bused%20joint%20and%20sequenced%20actions%20to%20run%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20international%20operation%20and%20debilitate%20the%20criminal%20infrastructure%20of%20multiple%20malware%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20operation%2C%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20shut%20down%20at%20least%20four%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-malware%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emalware%3C%2Fa%3E%20groups%20or%20%26quot%3Bdroppers%26quot%3B%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BIcedID%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSmokeloader%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BPikabot%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBumblebee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FBI%2C%20these%20droppers%2C%20designed%20to%20install%20malware%20onto%20computer%20systems%2C%20%26quot%3Binfected%20millions%20of%20computers%20and%20claimed%20countless%20victims%20around%20the%20world%20and%20throughout%20the%20United%20States%2C%20including%20a%20hospital%20network%2C%20which%20not%20only%20cost%20millions%20of%20dollars%20but%20alarmingly%20put%20people's%20lives%20at%20risk%20due%20to%20the%20compromised%20critical%20care%20online%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20taking%20down%20computer%20servers%2C%20which%20are%20affecting%20all%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wandt%2C%20who%20explained%20that%20the%20hackers%20behind%20the%20botnets%20are%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20for%20money%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20care%20who%20they%20go%20for%20or%20how%20they%20get%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20my%20grandmother%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20large%20bank.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWandt%20and%20other%20experts%20said%20the%20takedown%20of%20100%20malicious%20servers%20is%20a%20small%20number%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20vast%20number%20of%20servers%20that%20run%20botnets%20around%20the%20globe%20but%20that%20it's%20nonetheless%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20it%20was%20a%20small%20number%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20fraud%20that%20it%20was%20committing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wandt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d901e093-99a9-491d-b53d-a08f70169714%5C%22%3ERansomware%20'wreaking%20havoc%20around%20the%20world'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETracy%20Beth%20Mitrano%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20policy%20expert%20and%20a%20visiting%20professor%20of%20information%20science%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Endgame%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20said%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20significant%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20total%20scope%20of%20the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcyberattacks-on-american-cities-responses-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERansomware%20has%20just%20been%20wreaking%20havoc%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitrano%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20ripping%20through%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitrano%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20US%20working%20with%20other%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20to%20combat%20cybercrime%20and%20called%20for%20international%20law%2C%20treaties%2C%20and%20agreements%20%26quot%3Bto%20establish%20rules%20of%20the%20road%20in%20cyberspace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20war%20will%20not%20be%20won%20until%20there%20are%20international%20laws%20and%20standards%20that%20bring%20countries%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mitrano.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitrano%20said%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Endgame%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20important%20first%20step%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCyber%20insecurity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20threats%20we%20face%20on%20the%20globe%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Holt%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20expert%20and%20professor%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Criminal%20Justice%20at%20Michigan%20State%20University%2C%20said%20the%20coordinated%20effort%20of%20countries%20around%20the%20globe%20working%20to%20fight%20cybercrime%20as%20was%20done%20in%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Endgame%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCybercrime%20is%20such%20a%20distributed%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20cybercriminals%20can%20target%20%26quot%3Banyone%20anywhere%20with%20relative%20ease%2C%20and%20the%20likelihood%20of%20detection%20is%20really%2C%20really%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20any%20attempt%20at%20cracking%20down%20on%20cybercrime%20is%20a%20positive%2C%20Holt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20net%20gain%20in%20terms%20of%20complicating%20networks%20or%20forcing%20short-term%20behavioral%20change%20on%20the%20market%20and%20the%20actors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Holt.%20%26quot%3BIt%20may%20not%20create%20these%20long-term%20sustained%20drop-offs%2C%20but%20it%20at%20least%20provides%20a%20short-term%20benefit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolt%20said%20he%20does%20not%20believe%20cybercrime%20will%20ever%20be%20stopped%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20I%20think%20we%20can%20do%20is%20produce%20complexities%20for%20the%20offender%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20them%20to%20actually%20engage%20in%20an%20offense%20like%20running%20a%20botnet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20problem%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20malware%20world%2C%20according%20to%20Holt%2C%20is%20that%20there%20is%20always%20a%20different%20iteration%20of%20malware%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20it%20has%20been%20ransomware%20primarily%2C%20but%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20an%20eventual%20pivot%20away%20from%20ransomware%20to%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20exactly%20what%20that%20something%20else%20is%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-cyber-crime-phishing-malware-artificial-intelligence-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bwill%20certainly%20simplify%20the%20process%26quot%3B%20for%20cyberattackers%2C%20said%20Holt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECybercriminals%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20have%20the%20same%20degree%20of%20difficulty%20or%20barriers%20to%20entry%20that%20we%20had%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20the%2090s%2C%20and%20even%20the%20early%202000s%2C%26quot%3B%20Holt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it's%20flattened%20to%20a%20point%20where%20as%20long%20as%20you%20have%20money%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20personal%20data%2C%20you%20buy%20credit%20card%20numbers%2C%20rent%20out%20denial%20of%20service%20attacks%20on%20demand%20or%20botnets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20don't%20even%20need%20to%20know%20what%20you're%20doing.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20have%20a%20cursory%20understanding%20and%20dollars%20in%20your%20pocket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20results%20of%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Endgame%26quot%3B%20last%20month%2C%20Wray%2C%20the%20FBI%20director%2C%20vowed%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20against%20borderless%20cybercrime%20does%20not%20end%20here%2C%20and%20the%20FBI%20is%20committed%20to%20tackling%20this%20ever-evolving%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foperation-endgame-fbi-europol-cybercrime-malware-cybersecurity-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718794801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663511b00dfb1341e9026881%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%2