e%20are%20as%20large%20as%20Otium's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22balcony%20lounge%20chairs%20of%20Silver%20Ray's%20Otium%20Suite%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671ec8e087acd2be9b4ce04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20balcony%20has%20270-degree%20views.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20need%20to%20hit%20the%20pool%20deck%20when%20your%20431-square-foot%20balcony%20has%20a%20private%20hot%20tub%2C%20lounge%20chairs%2C%20and%20an%20outdoor%20dining%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20compare%2C%20Silver%20Ray's%20smallest%20suites%20come%20with%20a%2053-square-foot%20balcony.%20Size%20does%20matter%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20private%20hot%20tub%20is%20included%20in%20the%20suite%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%242%2C430%20per%20person%20and%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22balcony%20with%20hot%20tub%20and%20dining%20set%20of%20Silver%20Ray's%20Otium%20Suite%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671ecba087acd2be9b4ce74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%202024%2C%20prices%20per%20person%20for%20available%20itineraries%20range%20from%20%2417%2C000%20for%20a%20seven-day%20cruise%20to%20%2433%2C200%20for%20an%2011-day%20one%20with%20the%20most%20inclusive%20package.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHey%2C%20at%20least%20the%20cost%20includes%20a%20%24399%20spa%20treatment%20per%20person%2C%20too.%20Maybe%20a%20luxurious%20massage%20would%20help%20melt%20away%20the%20stress%20of%20the%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-ultra-luxury-cruise-cabin-silversea-new-ship-suite-2024-6