Other%20hospitals%20in%20Delhi%20are%20also%20seeing%20many%20admissions%20due%20to%20heatstrokes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ajay%20Shukla%2C%20medical%20superintendent%20of%20the%20state-run%20hospital%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%2022%20people%20had%20been%20admitted%20after%20they%20suffered%20a%20heatstroke.%20%26quot%3BFive%20patients%20died%20and%2012%20or%2013%20patients%20are%20on%20ventilator%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20doctor%20warned%20that%20the%20mortality%20rate%20in%20heatstroke%20cases%20is%20quite%20high%20--%20about%2060-70%20per%20cent.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20patient%20is%20brought%20late%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20one%20organ%20after%20the%20other%20starts%20failing.%20There%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness.%20A%20lot%20of%20these%20patients%20are%20migrant%20labourers.%20Also%2C%20the%20symptoms%20(of%20heatstroke)%20can%20be%20easily%20missed%20or%20mistaken%20for%20something%20else.%20It's%20only%20when%20patients%20faint%20that%20their%20relatives%20feel%20that%20hospitalisation%20is%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shukla%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20heatstroke.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20educate%20people.%20Instead%20of%20rushing%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20if%20you%20suspect%20that%20a%20person%20is%20suffering%20from%20heatstroke%2C%20you%20must%20start%20the%20cooling%20there%20and%20then.%20Use%20water%2C%20ice%2C%20while%20trying%20to%20get%20them%20to%20the%20hospital.%20We%20have%20also%20equipped%20ambulances%20so%20that%20they%20can%20start%20cooling%20immediately%20after%20they%20reach%20the%20patients.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20residents%20are%20reeling%20under%20an%20unrelenting%20heatwave%20for%20nearly%20a%20month%20now.%20Minimum%20temperatures%20in%20the%20city%20have%20crossed%20the%2035%20degrees%20mark%20--%20several%20degrees%20above%20normal%20--%20and%20maximum%20temperatures%20hover%20around%20the%2045%20degrees%20mark.%20Tap%20water%20is%20hot%20through%20the%20day%2C%20and%20even%20air-conditioners%20are%20struggling%20to%20bring%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20has%20said%20in%20its%20forecast%20that%20heatwave%20conditions%20are%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20most%20parts%20of%20north%20India%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours%20and%20abate%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20is%20leading%20to%20the%20abnormally%20warm%20nights%2C%20Rajneesh%20Sareen%20of%20the%20Delhi-based%20thinktank%20Centre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20(CSE)%20has%20an%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20construction%20and%20concretisation%20in%20big%20cities%20like%20Delhi%20has%20significantly%20gone%20up.%20Concrete%20buildings%20absorb%20heat%20through%20the%20day%20and%20release%20it%20at%20night.%20This%20is%20why%20minimum%20temperatures%20are%20rising%20in%20big%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sareen%2C%20programme%20director%20for%20Sustainable%20Habitat%20Programme%20at%20CSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20he%20said%2C%20daytime%20temperatures%20would%20be%20high%2C%20but%20people%20would%20get%20some%20relief%20at%20night.%20%26quot%3BBut%20nowadays%2C%20ACs%20are%20exploding%20because%20of%20a%20heat%20island%20effect.%20Construction%20in%20Delhi%20is%20going%20up%20and%20the%20green%20area%20is%20reducing.%20The%20construction%20of%20high-rises%20is%20also%20affecting%20wind%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20use%20of%20concrete%20has%20to%20be%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718793660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5rng0mfo_delhi-heat_625x300_19_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-heatwave-5-dead-12-on-life-support-as-delhi-reels-under-heatwave-that-has-no-end-5922977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20people%20have%20died%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%20and%20at%20least%2012%20are%20on%20life%20support