ives%20linked%20to%20American%20fugitive%20John%20Mark%20Dougan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F05%2F29%2Fbusiness%2Fmark-dougan-russia-disinformation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elinked%20to%20a%20network%20of%20Russian%20propaganda%20websites%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20local%20news%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDougan%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20a%20Florida%20deputy%20sheriff%2C%20fled%20to%20Moscow%20after%20being%20investigated%20for%20wiretapping%20and%20extortion.%20Mainstream%20media%20outlets%2C%20including%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20have%20extensively%20covered%20Dougan%20and%20his%20disinformation%20empire%20%E2%80%94%20reporting%20that%20AI%20chatbots%20should%20be%20easily%20able%20to%20access%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsGuard%20tested%2010%20AI%20chatbots%2C%20including%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT-4%3B%20You.com's%20Smart%20Assistant%2C%20xAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fx-wants-advertisers-to-use-grok-they-are-not-interested-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Inflection's%20Pi%2C%20Mistral's%20le%20Chat%2C%20Microsoft's%20Copilot%2C%20Meta%20AI%2C%20Anthropic's%20Claude%2C%20Google's%20Gemini%2C%20and%20Perplexity's%20answer%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Google%20said%20the%20company%20is%20working%20%26quot%3Bconstantly%26quot%3B%20to%20improve%20Gemini's%20responses%20and%20prevent%20harmful%20content%20from%20generating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20teams%20are%20reviewing%20this%20report%20and%20have%20already%20taken%20action%20on%20several%20responses%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20other%20companies%20immediately%20responded%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsGuard%20proposed%20570%20total%20prompts%2C%20issuing%20each%20chatbot%2057%20prompts%20each.%20The%20prompts%2