n%20Oxford%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66715d4e764df161125aa29f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Radcliffe%20Camera%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20buildings%20in%20Oxford.%3Cp%3EUCG%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConnecting%20my%20iPhone%20to%20the%20audio%20system%20was%20simple%20and%20there%20are%20convenient%20twin%20cordless%20charging%20pads%20built%20into%20the%20central%20console.%20The%20soundtrack%20for%20our%20trip%20included%20Dua%20Lipa's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERadical%20Optimism%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20latest%20Pet%20Shop%20Boys%20album%2C%20%26quot%3BNonetheless.%26quot%3B%20Both%20sounded%20great%20through%20the%20car's%20array%20of%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20found%20incongruous%2C%20though%2C%20was%20the%20fake%20wood%20paneling%20on%20the%20dashboard.%20It%20feels%20completely%20out%20of%20place%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20why%20it's%20there.%20(Tesla%20wisely%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bwood%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-3-highland-update-photos-price-features-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModel%203%20refresh%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23fef586%5C%22%3ESeems%20to%20be%20some%20debate%20about%20the%20wood.%20Some%20folks%20say%20it's%20real%20wood%20with%20a%20veneer%2C%20others%20say%20it's%20fake.%20Let's%20hedge%20it%20if%20we%20don't%20know%20for%20sure.%20%3C%2Fmark%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fteslamotorsclub.com%2Ftmc%2Fthreads%2Fdid-a-wood-dash-trim-delete-today.297047%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23fef586%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fteslamotorsclub.com%2Ftmc%2Fthreads%2Fdid-a-wood-dash-trim-delete-today.297047%2F%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Telsa%20Model%203%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666826e9764df16112586db4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20the%20Telsa%20Model%203.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla's%20interior%20is%20dominated%20by%20an%20enormous%20touchscreen%20that%20controls%20every%20function%20of%20the%20car.%20It%20serves%20up%20a%20cavalcade%20of%20information%20and%20I%20often%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20hit%20the%20right%20bit%20of%20the%20screen%20without%20taking%20my%20eyes%20off%20the%20road%2C%20though%20I%20admit%20it%20makes%20navigation%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Model%203%20touchscreen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670a866ed9a404d829e87cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Model%203's%20touchscreen%20is%20big.%20Really%20big.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lane%20assist%20and%20hazard%20warning%20technology%20can%20often%20be%20too%20clever%20for%20its%20own%20good%2C%20getting%20overexcited%20about%20supposed%20dangers%20that%20are%20nothing%20of%20the%20sort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trunk%20is%20cavernous%2C%20and%20could%20easily%20accommodate%20the%20luggage%20of%20four%20or%20even%20five%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Model%203%20trunk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66682ed8e079049018179e9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20trunk%20of%20the%20Tesla%20Model%203%20could%20fit%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20luggage.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Model%203%20is%20a%20very%20quiet%20drive