er%20edits%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20scenes%20would%20be%20deemed%20offensive.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20scene%20where%20a%20character%20threatens%20to%20kill%20his%20daughter%20while%20invoking%20God's%20name%20was%20pointed%20out%20as%20potentially%20problematic.%20The%20court%20suggested%20that%20removing%20this%20line%20would%20not%20compromise%20the%20filmmakers'%20creative%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20BP%20Colabawalla%20and%20Firdosh%20Pooniwalla%20said%20that%20the%20film%2C%20starring%20actor%20Annu%20Kapoor%2C%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bthinking%20movie%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20engage%20the%20audience%20intellectually%20rather%20than%20being%20a%20mindless%20entertainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20movie%20is%20in%20fact%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20women.%20The%20movie%20has%20a%20Maulana%20misinterpreting%20the%20Quran%20and%20in%20fact%20one%20Muslim%20man%20objects%20to%20the%20same%20in%20the%20scene.%20So%20this%20shows%20that%20people%20should%20apply%20their%20mind%20and%20not%20blindly%20follow%20such%20Maulanas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20addressed%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20petitioners%2C%20who%20claimed%20the%20film%20was%20derogatory%20towards%20Muslims%20and%20distorted%20Islamic%20teachings.%20These%20objections%20led%20to%20the%20postponement%20of%20the%20film's%20release.%20However%2C%20after%20reviewing%20the%20film%20post%20the%20deletion%20of%20objectionable%20content%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20Central%20Board%20for%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%2C%20the%20court%20found%20no%20grounds%20to%20continue%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20the%20premature%20release%20of%20the%20film's%20trailer%20before%20CBFC%20certification%2C%20which%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20controversy.%20As%20a%20consequence%2C%20the%20court%20imposed%20a%20penalty%20on%20the%20filmmakers%20to%20be%20donated%20to%20a%20charity%20of%20the%20petitioners'%20choice%2C%20citing%20the%20%26quot%3Bunpaid%20publicity%26quot%3B%20the%20litigation%20had%20generated%20for%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BViolation%20was%20there%20vis-a-vis%20the%20trailer.%20So%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20something%20towards%20a%20charity%20of%20the%20petitioner's%20choice.%20Cost%20will%20have%20to%20be%20paid.%20This%20litigation%20has%20got%20the%20film%20so%20much%20unpaid%20publicity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20anything%20in%20the%20movie%20that%20would%20incite%20any%20violence.%20If%20we%20felt%20so%20we%20would%20be%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20object%20to%20it.%20Indian%20public%20is%20not%20so%20gullible%20or%20that%20silly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20judgment%20will%20be%20available%20on%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718790600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fkea19g7_hamare-baarah_625x300_03_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-dialogues-muted-court-clears-hamare-baarah-for-june-21-release-5922832%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20today%20permitted%20the%20release%20of%20the%20film%20'Hamare%20Baarah'%20on%20June%2021%20after%20the%20filmmakers%20agreed%20to%20make%20three%20changes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-dialogues-muted-court-clears-hamare-baarah-for-june-21-release-5922832%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-dialogues-muted-court-clears-hamare-baarah-for-june-21-release-5922832%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-dialogues-muted-court-clears-hamare-baarah-for-june-21-release-5922832%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20drone%20attack%20damage