0don't%20have%20barcodes%2C%20and%20many%20are%20sold%20by%20the%20pound%2C%20making%20accurate%20weighing%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20meant%20I%20had%20to%20enter%20PLU%20codes%20%E2%80%94%20those%20numbers%20on%20the%20stickers%20you%20find%20on%20produce%20%E2%80%94%20before%20placing%20it%20into%20the%20Dash%20cart's%20basket%20and%20weighing%20it%20using%20the%20built-in%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20bell%20peppers%20were%20priced%20per%20pepper%2C%20but%20I%20still%20had%20to%20find%20them%20on%20the%20Dash%20cart's%20screen%20before%20placing%20them%20in%20its%20basket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEntering%20codes%20for%20produce%20reminded%20me%20of%20using%20self-checkout%20at%20other%20grocery%20stores.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221054%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20screen%20of%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart%20displays%20a%20search%20function%20where%20users%20can%20enter%20a%20product's%20code%20or%20name%20via%20a%20keyboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66719614764df161125ab4e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECustomers%20use%20this%20on-screen%20keyboard%20to%20enter%20product%20names%20and%20codes%20before%20placing%20them%20in%20the%20cart's%20basket.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20self-checkout%20a%20lot%20at%20my%20local%20supermarket.%20Punching%20in%20codes%20for%20the%20bell%20peppers%20and%20other%20produce%20reminded%20me%20of%20that%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20made%20the%20Dash%20cart%20feel%20like%20a%20self-checkout%20on%20wheels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDash%20carts%20also%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bsales%20%26amp%3B%20deals%26quot%3B%20tab%20that%20changes%20as%20you%20move%20around%20the%20store.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221060%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bottles%20of%20juice%20on%20sale%20appear%20on%20the%20screen%20of%20the%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671995070a95768a3116636%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dash%20cart's%20screen%20shows%20you%20what's%20on%20sale%20around%20the%20store.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20selection%20of%20cranberry%20juice%20specials%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20popped%20up%20as%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20aisle%20where%20the%20products%20were%20located.%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20later%20as%20I%20walked%20down%20the%20snack%20aisle%20and%20past%20the%20cooler%20case%20for%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20products%20could%20be%20scanned%20via%20barcode%2C%20though%20some%20were%20easier%20than%20others.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20reporter%20scans%20a%20pack%20of%20tonic%20water%20with%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart.%20The%20barcode%20is%20on%20the%20bottom%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20scan%20the%20pack%20while%20keeping%20the%20glass%20bottles%20in%20place.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667196f6764df161125ab552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221054%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20products%20in%20Amazon%20Fresh%20just%20require%20a%20quick%20scan%20before%20you%20place%20them%20in%20the%20cart.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dash%20cart%20includes%20three%20scanners%3A%20Two%20front-facing%20ones%20above%20the%20basket%20and%20another%20downward-facing%20one%20under%20the%20handle.%20You%20could%20scan%20most%20of%20the%20packaged%20goods%20in%20the%20store%20using%20one%20of%20the%20three%20sensors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20the%20barcode%20on%20some%20products%20made%20scanning%20difficult%2C%20though.%20This%20four-pack%20of%20tonic%20water%20had%20its%20barcode%20on%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20cardboard%20holder%2C%20making%20it%20tough%20to%20scan%20while%20keeping%20the%20glass%20bottles%20from%20slipping%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20get%20any%20error%20messages%20when%20I%20rearranged%20items%20in%20the%20cart%20or%20put%20items%20that%20were%20already%20there%20in%20my%20shopping%20bag.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22772%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grocery%20items%20sit%20in%20a%20shopping%20bag%20in%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667199aa70a95768a311665d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221056%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20brought%20my%20own%20reusable%20shopping%20bag%20to%20Amazon%20Fresh.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20self-checkouts%20I've%20used%2C%20which%20give%20you%20an%20error%20message%20when%20you%20rearrange%20stuff%20in%20your%20bag%20or%20knock%20something%20over%2C%20the%20Dash%20cart%20didn't%20mind%20when%20I%20had%20to%20rearrange%20my%20purchases.%20I%20also%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20problems%20consolidating%20things%20into%20my%20shopping%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERemoving%20items%20required%20using%20the%20screen%20but%20was%20easy%20to%20do.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221372%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20reporter%20holds%20a%20can%20of%20hard%20seltzer%20over%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart%20before%20scanning%20it%20and%20putting%20it%20in%20the%20cart's%20basket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671b9a2a76074d191cced3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScanning%20items%20with%20the%20Dash%20cart%20was%20pretty%20easy%20once%20you%20got%20used%20to%20it.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20looking%20at%20the%20alcohol%20selection%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20see%20how%20hard%20it%20was%20to%20remove%20something%20from%20the%20cart%20and%20my%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20chose%20a%20can%20of%20hard%20seltzer%2C%20scanned%20it%2C%20and%20placed%20it%20in%20the%20Dash%20cart.%20Then%2C%20I%20picked%20it%20up%20out%20of%20the%20cart%20and%20put%20it%20back%20in%20the%20cooler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Dash%20cart%20asked%20me%20to%20confirm%20whether%20I%20had%20actually%20removed%20a%20product%20or%20not.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20screen%20of%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart%20shows%20a%20can%20of%20hard%20seltzer%20and%20asks%20the%20user%20to%20confirm%20how%20many%20cans%20they're%20purchasing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671b92b2efa138e0330ae79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221116%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20edit%20what%20was%20in%20my%20cart%20using%20the%20Dash%20cart's%20screen.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20screen%20popped%20up%20when%20I%20returned%20the%20can%20to%20the%20cooler.%20I%20confirmed%20that%20I%20had%20indeed%20removed%20it%20and%20proceeded%20to%20add%20a%20different%20choice%20to%20my%20cart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Dash%20cart%20didn't%20catch%20everything%2C%20though.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221410%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20reporter%20holds%20a%20box%20of%20Cheetos%20mac%20n'%20cheese%20behind%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66719718764df161125ab580%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221052%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20decided%20to%20see%20if%20the%20Dash%20cart%20would%20catch%20a%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20weight%20of%20my%20purchases%20and%20what%20was%20on%20the%20receipt.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20cart%20relies%20on%20its%20internal%20scale%20so%20much%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20there%20was%20a%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20items%20on%20the%20screen%20and%20what%20was%20actually%20in%20the%20basket.%20(No%2C%20I%20did%20not%20steal%20anything%2C%20and%20neither%20should%20you.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20scanned%20an%20item%2C%20then%20removed%20it%20from%20the%20Dash%20cart.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20reporter%20scans%20the%20barcode%20on%20a%20box%20of%20mac%20n'%20cheese%20using%20the%20scanner%20on%20an%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671979270a95768a31164fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20the%20scanner%20under%20the%20handle%20this%20time.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20by%20scanning%20this%20box%20of%20mac%20and%20cheese%20and%20placing%20it%20in%20the%20basket.%20Then%2C%20I%20put%20it%20back%20on%20the%20shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20this%20message%20flashed%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20I%20said%20that%20I%20hadn't%20removed%20anything.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221410%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Amazon%20Dash%20cart's%20screen%20shows%20a%20message%20that%20customers%20get%20when%20the%20cart%20senses%20that%20something%20unidentified%20has%20been%20placed%20inside%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66719666ed9a404d829ea9f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221046%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dash%20cart%20figured%20out%20that%20something%20was%20missing%2C%20but%20didn't%20question%20me%20more%20when%20I%20said%20nothing%20was%20gone.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20still%20getting%20charged%20for%20the%20mac%20and%20cheese%20even%20though%20it%20wasn't%20in%20my%20cart%20anymore.%20Once%20I%20hit%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20my%20receipt%20is%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20could%20keep%20shopping%2C%20and%20neither%20the%20cart%20nor%20the%20employee%20working%20the%20exit%20for%20Dash%20cart%20users%20caught%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20