what%20I%2C%20as%20a%20millennial%2C%20tell%20myself.%20But%20we're%20getting%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20constantly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoing-out-cute-top-replaced-fun-pant-tiktok-genz-millennial-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecycling%20through%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cultural%20trends%20that%20supposedly%20separate%20millennials%20from%20their%20younger%20Gen%20Z%20counterparts%20%E2%80%94%20how%20each%20generation%20parts%20their%20hair%2C%20where%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-called-old-by-gen-z-for-dancing-arms-overhead-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20their%20hands%20when%20they%20dance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20how%20they%20tuck%20their%20shirts%20in.%20The%20latest%20iteration%20of%20this%20back-and-forth%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoker-knows-generation-millennial-or-gen-z-based-on-socks-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerational%20debate%20over%20socks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Per%20TikTok%2C%20millennials%20date%20themselves%20by%20wearing%20short%20ankle%20socks%20instead%20of%20longer%20ones%20that%20come%20up%20closer%20to%20the%20calf.%20Ultimately%2C%20this%20isn't%20really%20about%20socks%20(though%20good%20luck%20with%20those%20tan%20lines%2C%20kids!).%20Rather%2C%20it%20signifies%20the%20uncomfortable%20fact%20of%20increasing%20age%20and%20all%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20it.%20The%20socks%20are%20a%20reminder%20that%20time%20comes%20for%20everyone%2C%20and%20in%20the%20era%20of%20social%20media%2C%20the%20ticking%20clock%20is%20online%20and%20in%20your%20face.%20The%20internet%20is%20fueling%20the%20millennials%20vs.%20Gen%20Z%20discourse%2C%20but%20underlying%20it%20is%20something%20deeper%3A%20millennials%20raging%20against%20the%20dying%20of%20the%20light.%20And%20there's%20money%20to%20be%20made%20from%20this%20fear%20of%20aging%20%E2%80%94%20because%20there%20always%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMillennials%20are%20trying%20to%20cope%20with%20getting%20old%2C%20and%20they%20are%20the%20first%20generation%20that%20is%20kind%20of%20getting%20old%20on%20display%20because%20we%20are%20in%20a%20hyperconnected%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Valeria%20Penttinen%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20Northern%20Illinois%20University%20who%20focuses%20on%20digital%20and%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAging%20can%20be%20anxiety-inducing.%20Wrinkles%20and%20aches%20and%20pains%20are%20signs%20that%20our%20bodies%20are%20decaying%2C%20manifestations%20of%20the%20reality%20that%20we're%20marching%20toward%20the%20Big%20Scary%20that%20is%20death.%20Our%20society%20puts%20a%20premium%20on%20youth%2C%20and%20as%20people%20get%20older%2C%20they're%20viewed%20as%20irrelevant%2C%20invisible%2C%20and%20obsolete.%20Next%20time%20you're%20at%20the%20pharmacy%2C%20take%20a%20stroll%20down%20the%20greeting-card%20aisle.%20You'll%20find%20a%20bunch%20of%20birthday%20cards%20with%20jokes%20about%20aging%20%E2%80%94%20LOL%2C%20you're%20getting%20slow%2C%20senile%2C%20irrelevant%2C%20asexual%2C%20incapable%2C%20grumpy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20those%20stereotypes%20are%20very%20deeply%20ingrained%20within%20all%20of%20us%20so%20that%20we%20almost%20sort%20of%20mistake%20them%20for%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Julie%20Erickson%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist%20in%20Toronto%20who%20focuses%20on%20adults%20and%20older%20adults%20and%20a%20coauthor%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Aging%20Well%20Workbook%20for%20Anxiety%20and%20Depression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20alleviate%20some%20of%20our%20anxieties%20around%20aging%2C%20we%20try%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20times.%20We%20update%20our%20wardrobes%2C%20consume%20the%20latest%20culture%2C%20and%20stock%20up%20on%20endless%20skincare%20products.%20Essentially%2C%20we%20attempt%20to%20spend%20our%20way%20to%20eternal%20youth%20and%20beauty.%20For%20brands%2C%20millennials'%20existential%20dread%20represents%20a%20lucrative%20opportunity%20to%20sell%2C%20especially%20in%20an%20era%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrader-joes-mini-tote-bags-stanley-cups-tiktok-consumerism-marketing-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efads%20cycle%20through%20faster%20than%20ever%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20look%20at%20instincts%20that%20come%20along%20with%20feeling%20scared%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20when%20our%20fight%2C%20flight%2C%20freeze%20response%20kicks%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Erickson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20aspect%20of%20that%20response%20is%20the%20fight%20response%2C%20which%20gets%20us%20mobilized%20and%20activated%20to%20try%20to%20do%20things%20to%20defend%20against%20a%20perceived%20threat.%20That%20can%20include%20throwing%20money%20at%20a%20quote%2C%20unquote%2C%20problem%2C%20trying%20to%20spend%20your%20way%20into%20alleviating%20some%20of%20your%20fears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20example%20of%20this%20is%20probably%20the%20antiaging%20industry%2C%20which%20makes%20billions%20of%20dollars%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fthe-goods%2F2022%2F7%2F28%2F23219258%2Fanti-aging-cream-expensive-scam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyear%20trying%20to%20convince%20us%20we%20can%20achieve%20the%20impossible%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20staying%20young%20forever.%20The%20message%20isn't%20exactly%20that%20you're%20not%20supposed%20to%20get%20older%3B%20it's%20just%20that%20you're%20not%20supposed%20to%20look%20like%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrities-who-dont-aged-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAge%20like%20J.Lo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20basically%2C%20and%20blow%20a%20bunch%20of%20money%20on%20creams%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotox-injections-fillers-plastic-surgery-gen-z-social-media-filters-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjections%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20keep%20wrinkles%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20a%20'40%20is%20the%20new%2030'%20vibe%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20if%20only%20because%20millennials%20are%20more%20obsessed%20with%20health%20and%20wellness%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Miraflor%2C%20the%20chief%20brand%20officer%20at%20Hannah%20Grey%2C%20a%20venture-capital%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20industry%20is%20hardly%20the%20only%20one%20that%20capitalizes%20on%20the%20unfeasible%20pursuit%20of%20youth.%20So%20much%20of%20consumerism%20depends%20on%20novelty%20%E2%80%94%20the%20latest%20fitness%20craze%20or%20fashion%20trend%20or%20musical%20artist.%20Much%20of%20that%20novelty%20hinges%20on%20new%20generations%20and%20the%20interests%20and%20inclinations%20of%20young%20people%2C%20namely%2C%20the%2018-to-34%20demographic%20marketers%20so%20highly%20covet.%20For%20millennials%2C%20it's%20awkward%20to%20age%20out%20of%20that%20demo%20and%20no%20longer%20be%20the%20hot%2C%20new%20thing.%20It's%20jarring%20to%20realize%20Justin%20Timberlake's%20new%20tour%20and%20Usher's%20Super%20Bowl%20performance%20are%20nostalgia%20plays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20struggle%20to%20stay%20young%20means%20that%20many%20millennials%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20chase%20the%20hot%2C%20new%20thing.%20Sure%2C%20they%20may%20not%20want%20to%20dress%20%3Cem%3Eexactly%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20the%20kids%20these%20days%2C%20but%20they%20wouldn't%20mind%20shaving%20five%20or%2010%20years%20off%20by%20wearing%20looser%20jeans%20or%20taller%20socks%20or%20a%20baggier%20T-shirt.%20Your%20birth%20certificate%20may%20say%20you're%2033%2C%20but%20your%20sneakers%20don't%20have%20to.%20It's%20tempting%20to%20try%20to%20hold%20on%2C%20especially%20with%20an%20influencer%20online%20explaining%20to%20you%20how%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMillennials%20are%20having%20an%20existential%20sort%20of%20crisis%20with%20regard%20to%20their%20loss%20of%20the%20grip%20on%20youth%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Claire%20Tassin%2C%20a%20retail%20and%20e-commerce%20analyst%20at%20Morning%20Consult%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20beneficial%20for%20brands%20that%20at%20least%20the%20online%20discourse%20has%20millennials%20looking%20to%20Gen%20Z%20for%20trends.%20Because%20if%20they%20can%20sell%20all%20of%20us%20the%20same%20stuff%2C%20that's%20more%20cost-efficient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJean%20Twenge%2C%20a%20psychologist%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D095908a1241d3f10f1aad7a63c6f4c809cb97a516da7dcaf7a65359febd2bced%26postID%3D66689950e7e1e0003ff2c026%26postSlug%3Dmillennials-gen-z-socks-jeans-brands-aging-cash-advertising-2024-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FGenerations-Differences-Millennials-Silents_and-Americas%252Fdp%252F1982181613%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGenerations%3A%20The%20Real%20Differences%20Between%20Gen%20Z%2C%20Millennials%2C%20Gen%20X%2C%20Boomers%2C%20and%20Silents%20%E2%80%94%20and%20What%20They%20Mean%20for%20America's%20Future%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20pointed%20out%20that%20generations%20realizing%20they're%20not%20the%20young%20trendsetters%20anymore%20is%20not%20new.%20Gen%20X%20used%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20before%20then%2C%20boomers.%20But%20social%20media%20does%20really%20put%20the%20issue%20on%20overdrive%20and%20has%20warped%20millennials'%20shift%20into%20the%20has-beens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSocial%20media%20really%20ramps%20up%20the%20generational%20conversation%20and%2C%20sometimes%2C%20the%20generational%20conflict%2C%20whether%20that's%20over%20serious%20issues%2C%20like%20the%20economy%20and%20student%20loans%2C%20or%20things%20like%20fashion%20and%20consumer%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20chatter%20can%20be%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20that%20deep%20that%20your%20side%20part%20means%20you're%20over%2030.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20somewhat%20mortifying%20when%20you%20realize%20that%20you're%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20trend%2C%20and%20you%20have%20that%20constant%20reminder%20in%20your%20TikTok%20or%20Twitter%20feed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20what's%20going%20on%20coolnesswise%20and%20to%20know%20whether%20you're%20in%20or%20out.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20older%20people%20lost%20touch%20with%20youth%20culture%20because%20they%20didn't%20really%20see%20it%20in%20their%20day-to-day%2C%20but%20now%2C%20every%20shift%20in%20style%20is%20blasted%20right%20into%20millennials'%20feeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20social%20media%2C%20because%20we%20can%20see%20what's%20new%2C%20what's%20trending%2C%20we%20can%20adapt%20our%20behaviors%20a%20bit%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20Penttinen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nature%20of%20internet%20culture%2C%20much%20of%20which%20was%20created%20by%20millennials%2C%20puts%20a%20unique%20bent%20on%20the%20discourse%20and%20how%20creators%20and%20influencers%20address%20millennials.%20For%20a%20generation%20raised%20on%20a%20sense%20of%20irony%20and%20mockery%2C%20poking%20fun%20at%20their%20uncoolness%20can%20be%20an%20effective%20play%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20even%20persuade%20them%20to%20give%20some%20new%20trend%20a%20shot%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20loop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20the%20self-deprecation%20part%20of%20it%20and%20leaning%20into%20it%20versus%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20millennial%20who's%20aging%20feel%20better%20about%20aging%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20almost%20like%20let's%20have%20some%20fun%20with%20it%20and%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20you're%20entering%20into%20another%20phase%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harley%20Block%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20a%20cofounder%20of%20IF7%2C%20a%20brand-consultancy%20firm%20that%20focuses%20on%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoel%20Steckel%2C%20a%20marketing%20professor%20at%20New%20York%20University%2C%20told%20me%20marketers%20have%20to%20talk%20differently%20to%20millennials%20than%20they%20did%20generations%20past%20because%20the%20context%20around%20them%20is%20different%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20mistrust%20of%20information%2C%20they%20experienced%20an%20economic%20crisis%2C%20and%20the%20market%20is%20more%20crowded%20with%20brands.%20They%20think%20more%20about%20what%20brands%20say%20%3Cem%3Eabout%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethem%20to%20the%20outside%20world%20than%20what%20the%20brand%20says%3Cem%3E%20to%3C%2Fem%3E%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20changing%20more%20throughout%20time%20is%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20consumers%20will%20use%20the%20information%20that%20the%20brand%20signals%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20using%20it%20less.%20They're%20using%20it%20less%20with%20respect%20to%20what%20the%20brand%20signals%20to%20them%20and%20more%20of%20what%20the%20use%20of%20the%20brand%20signals%20to%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20what%20millennials%20would%20like%20the%20clothes%20they%20wear%20or%20the%20products%20they%20use%20to%20say%20about%20them%20is%20that%20they're%20still%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20and%20shifting%20contexts%20are%20not%20the%20only%20things%20making%20millennials'%20aging-out%20experience%20a%20bit%20different%20from%20what%20it%20was%20for%20generations%20past%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20just%20talking%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20think%20everything%20is%20about%20them.%20(I%20kid%2C%20kind%20of.)%20Millennials%20have%20been%20defined%20by%20their%20youth.%20They%20were%20the%20generation%20putting%20off%20marriage%2C%20having%20children%2C%20and%20buying%20a%20home.%20In%20the%20popular%20narrative%2C%20that's%20not%20because%20they%20graduated%20into%20a%20recession%20but%20because%20they%20were%20splurging%20on%20Starbucks.%20Millennials%20supposedly%20needed%20to%20be%20coddled%20with%20participation%20trophies%2C%20and%20whenever%20they%20%3Cem%3Edid%20%3C%2Fem%3Edo%20something%20grown-up%2C%20they%20got%20to%20call%20it%20%26quot%3Badulting.%26quot%3B%20It%20feels%20like%20no%20matter%20how%20old%20millennials%20get%20%E2%80%94%20and%20plenty%20of%20them%20are%20in%20their%20early%2040s%20at%20this%20point%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cultural%20image%20of%20the%20avocado-toast-obsessed%2020-something%20paying%20back%20their%20student%20loans%20via%20a%20gig%20job%20persisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevon%20Price%2C%20a%20social-psychology%20professor%20and%20author%20at%20Loyola%20University%20Chicago's%20School%20of%20Continuing%20and%20Professional%20Studies%2C%20said%20millennials%20were%20the%20last%20generation%20to%20grow%20up%20with%20a%20real%20set%20of%20life%20milestones%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20hit%2C%20and%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20them%2C%20those%20checkpoints%20have%20taken%20longer%20than%20they'd%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20completely%20bottomed%20out%20on%20us%20just%20as%20we%20were%20coming%20into%20that%20adulthood%20that%20we%20were%20told%20to%20expect%20and%20earn.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20gave%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20weird%20neuroses%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20arrested%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20way%2C%20we%20got%20really%20attached%20to%20an%20idea%20of%20ourselves%20as%20perpetually%20young%20because%20we%20didn't%20have%20those%20milestones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20tables%20have%20turned%20%E2%80%94%20millennials%20are%20no%20longer%20%26quot%3Bthe%20youngs%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20they're%20not%20quite%20%26quot%3Bthe%20olds%2C%26quot%3B%20either%20because%20they%20don't%20feel%20like%20it%20or%20because%20society%20doesn't%20treat%20them%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20buy%20our%20way%20into%20looking%20and%20seeming%20young%20because%20then%20we%20can%20still%20feel%20like%20it's%20OK.%20It's%20still%20just%20a%20big%20party.%20We're%20still%20having%20fun%20here.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20mature%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20stereotype%2C%20many%20millennials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-wealth-surprising-finance-earning-salaries-great-resignation-job-hop-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earen't%20doing%20too%20poorly%3C%2Fa%3E%20financially%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20companies%20to%20try%20to%20get%20their%20money.%20Over%20half%20of%20millennials%20have%20homes.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20stable%20and%20lucrative%20jobs%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-z-stock-market-baby-boomers-wealth-investing-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolid%20investment%20portfolios%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20gotten%20married%20and%20started%20families%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20forced%20some%20acknowledgment%20of%20a%20generational%20split.%20Once%20children%20come%20into%20the%20picture%2C%20some%20of%20the%20youth%20and%20trend%20chasing%20is%20diminished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20dividing%20line%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20is%20whether%20they%20have%20kids.%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20why%20we%20have%20the%20whole%20concept%20of%20mom%20jeans%2C%26quot%3B%20Twenge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20kids%2C%20millennials%20may%20be%20more%20tempted%20to%20try%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20times%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20just%20that%20your%20child%20is%20going%20to%20say%20you%20dress%20lame%3B%20it's%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20post%20their%20critique%20on%20TikTok.%20So%20now%2C%20Miraflor%20said%2C%20you%20get%20millennial%20dads%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Ballowed%20to%20be%20cool%20and%20smart%20and%20empathetic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20of%20the%20life%20milestones%20of%20marriage%20and%20having%20children%20being%20delayed%20means%20that%20the%20goalposts%20of%20'growing%20up%20and%20being%20an%20adult'%20moves%20along%20with%20that%2C%20almost%20out%20of%20necessity%2C%26quot%3B%20Miraflor%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%2C%20compounded%20with%20the%20pandemic%20that%20was%20timed%20right%20when%20many%20millennials%20were%20reaching%20middle%20age%2C%20means%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20nuance%20and%20texture%20required%20for%20mass%20millennial%20marketing.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20worse%20things%20one%20could%20do%20than%20buy%20a%20new%20outfit%20or%20some%20beauty%20cream%20to%20feel%20better%20about%20themselves%20and%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20older.%20Worst-case%20scenario%2C%20you%20wind%20up%20being%20a%20living%2C%20breathing%20version%20of%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-buscemi-how-do-you-do-fellow-kids-halloween-costume-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20do%20you%20do%2C%20fellow%20kids%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20meme.%20It's%20embarrassing%2C%20but%20you'll%20survive.%20Best-case%20scenario%2C%20the%20purchase%20perks%20you%20up%20for%20a%20time%2C%20and%20maybe%20someone%20asks%20for%20your%20ID%2C%20a%20serious%20over-25%20thrill.%20But%20you%20can't%20spend%20your%20way%20out%20of%20aging%2C%20as%20much%20as%20corporate%20America%20would%20like%20you%20to%20think%20you%20can%2C%20unless%20you're%20Gwen%20Stefani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Erickson%2C%20the%20psychologist%20who%20focuses%20on%20aging%2C%20for%20some%20tips%20on%20dealing%20with%20getting%20older%20that%20do%20not%20involve%20opening%20up%20our%20wallets.%20She%20said%20the%20first%20piece%20is%20to%20unpack%20what%20your%20beliefs%20about%20aging%20are.%20What's%20the%20narrative%20you're%20telling%20yourself%3F%20That%20life%20will%20get%20boring%2C%20that%20you'll%20be%20lonely%20or%20become%20irrelevant%3F%20Try%20to%20look%20at%20some%20exceptions%20to%20those%20beliefs%2C%20like%20Martha%20Stewart%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-sports-illustrated-swimsuit-cover-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20cover%20of%20Sports%20Illustrated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20people%20who%20have%20had%20second%20and%20third%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20your%20own%20aging%20thus%20far.%20Are%20there%20aspects%20of%20being%2020%20that%20you're%20actually%20really%20happy%20to%20leave%20behind%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BStart%20to%20look%20at%20the%20evidence%20from%20your%20own%20life%20to%20say%2C%20'Sure%2C%20there's%20certain%20things%20that%20maybe%20have%20gotten%20harder%20or%20more%20complicated%20or%20difficult%2C%20but%20are%20there%20things%20about%20my%20own%20aging%20process%20that%20have%20been%20areas%20of%20growth%20or%20discovery%20or%20developing%20new%20strengths%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20sugarcoating%20it%3A%20Aging%20feels%20scary%2C%20and%20death%20is%20terrifying.%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20do%20make%20the%20discourse%20on%20all%20this%20worse.%20The%20jeans%20thing%20was%20inevitable%2C%20but%20the%20socks%20thing%3F%20Come%20on.%20Many%20of%20these%20generational%20divides%20are%20made%20up%20anyway.%20And%20if%20you're%20a%20smug%20Gen%20Z%20now%2C%20Gen%20Alpha%20is%20coming%20up%20right%20behind%20you%2C%20so%20be%20prepared%20to%20feel%20cringe%20or%20whatever%20their%20word%20for%20it%20is%20in%205%20to%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20sound%20anti-capitalist%20here%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20worth%20remembering%20who%20the%20real%20enemy%20is%2C%20or%20not%20the%20enemy%2C%20per%20se%2C%20but%20the%20entity%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on.%20Gen%20Z%2C%20be%20nice%20to%20your%20friendly%20millennial%20next%20door%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%20And%20both%20of%20you%2C%20be%20skeptical%20of%20that%20not-so-friendly%20company%20advertising%20to%20you%20on%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%20or%20TV.%20They%20make%20money%20only%20if%20you%20buy%20something%20new%2C%20and%20making%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20falling%20behind%20the%20times%20or%20presenting%20you%20with%20a%20hot%2C%20new%20trend%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20is%20a%20way%20to%20accomplish%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20hey%2C%20once%20your%20clothes%20go%20out%20of%20style%2C%20hold%20on%20to%20them%20even%20if%20you%20swap%20them%20out.%20They'll%20probably%20come%20back%20around%20in%2015%20years%2C%20and%20you%20can%20save%20yourself%20some%20money%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-z-socks-jeans-brands-aging-cash-advertising-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718790421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c6720764df1611259fa04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-z-socks-jeans-brands-aging-cash-advertising-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20problem%20with%20millennials%20isn't%20skinny%20jeans%20or%20ankle%20socks.%20It's%20that%20aging%20is%20terrifying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-z-socks-jeans-brands-aging-cash-advertising-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Viggo%20Mortensen%2C%20Clive%20Owen%2C%20Daniel%20Bruhl%20to%20Be%20Honored%20at%20Karlovy%20Vary%20Film%20Festival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718790300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%