0significantly%2C%20it%20has%20never%20been%20won%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20hope%20that%20Mrs%20Choudhary%20and%20her%20family%20connections%20will%20bring%20not%20only%20the%20Tosham%20seat%20but%20also%20a%20sizeable%20chunk%20of%20Jat%20votes%20that%20the%20party%20has%20been%20courting%20for%20several%20years%2C%20but%20now%20seems%20to%20be%20slipping%20through%20its%20fingers%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20farmers'%20ongoing%20protests%20against%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20-%20at%20the%20central%20and%20state%20levels%20-%20has%20been%20facing%20flak%20from%20Jat%20voters%2C%20who%20are%20largely%20farmers%2C%20over%20various%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20demand%20for%20legal%20backing%20for%20MSP%2C%20or%20minimum%20support%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20the%20Sonipat%20and%20Rohtak%20regions%2C%20where%20some%20villages%20even%20refused%20to%20vote%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Sonipat%20and%20Rohtak%20have%2018%20Assembly%20segments%20between%20them%2C%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20only%20four%20(post-poll%20ally%20JJP%20got%20one%20more)%20in%20the%20last%20state%20election%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20swept%2012.%20The%20BJP%20could%20have%20used%20those%2012%20seats%20after%20finishing%20six%20below%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2046%20in%20that%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESigning%20Mrs%20Choudhary%20and%20her%20family's%20political%20clout%20among%20Jats%20could%20also%20help%20the%20BJP%20overcome%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20JJP%2C%20its%20former%20ally%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20which%20was%20the%20party's%20Jat%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Bleeding%20Leaders%20Again%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20the%20loss%20is%20acute%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%20party%20will%20want%20to%20build%20on%20impressive%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20to%20push%20the%20BJP%20out%20of%20power%20in%20the%20state%20p