0open%20market.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20also%20arrested%20a%20businessman%2C%20Bakibur%20Rahman%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20probe%20into%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sengupta%20was%20earlier%20questioned%20by%20the%20probe%20agency%20in%202019%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Rose%20Valley%20chit%20fund%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718786580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbjigms2_rituparna-sengupta-facebook_625x300_31_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-actor-rituparna-sengupta-questioned-by-probe-agency-in-ration-scam-5922399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Popular%20Bengali%20actor%20Rituparna%20Sengupta%20was%20today%20questioned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20ration%20distribution%20scam%20in%20West%20Bengal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-actor-rituparna-sengupta-questioned-by-probe-agency-in-ration-scam-5922399%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-actor-rituparna-sengupta-questioned-by-probe-agency-in-ration-scam-5922399%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-actor-rituparna-sengupta-questioned-by-probe-agency-in-ration-scam-5922399%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20raise%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20cr%20via%20long-term%20bonds%20in%20FY25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718786558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F23%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1700736920-4358.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fstate-bank-of-india-to-raise-up-to-rs-20-000-cr-via-