ry%22%3A%22Renukaswamy%2C%20a%20fan%20of%20Sandalwood%20star%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%2C%20was%20killed%20after%20posting%20offensive%20remarks%20about%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20Darshan's%20girlfriend.%20The%20murder%20led%20to%20Darshan's%20arrest%20and%20sparked%20outrage%20on%20social%20media%20and%20protests%20in%20Karnataka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%20Among%20Top%20150%20Cities%20Across%20The%20World%20For%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20cities%20in%20India%20have%20been%20ranked%20among%20the%20best%20for%20students%20in%20the%20Quacquarelli%20Symonds%20(QS)%20Best%20Cities%20Rankings%202025%20that%20has%20a%20list%20of%20150%20cities.%20Delhi%20is%20at%20111th%20spot%2C%20followed%20by%20Mumbai%20at%20113%2C%20Bengaluru%20at%20130%20and%20Chennai%20at%20140.%20The%20rankings%20show%20that%20Delhi%20and%20Bengaluru%20have%20made%20significant%20leap%20in%20the%20rankings%20-%20by%2021%20and%2017%20places%20respectively.%20The%20QS%20rankings%20take%20into%20consideration%20six%20indicators%20like%20university%20ranking%2C%20student%20mix%2C%20employer%20activity%2C%20desirability%2C%20affordability%20and%20student%20view.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20affordability%2C%20Delhi%20comes%20on%20top%20among%20the%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20four%20cities%20score%20less%20than%2030%20in%20desirability%20and%20high%20on%20employer%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.topuniversities.com%2Fcity-rankings%3Ftab%3Dindicators%26countries%3DIndia%26sort_by%3Drank%26order_by%3Dasc%5C%22%3EOn%20its%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20QS%20Rankings%20said%20that%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20list%2C%20each%20city%20must%20have%20a%20population%20of%20over%20250%2C000%2C%20and%20be%20home%20to%20at%20least%20two%20universities%20featured%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20of%20their%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20London%20retained%20its%20top%20spot%20for%20sixth%20year%20in%20a%20row%2C%20followed%20by%20Tokyo%20and%20Seoul.%20Munich%20is%20at%20number%20four%2C%20while%20Melbourne%20at%20number%205.%20Sydney%2C%20Paris%2C%20Zurich%20and%20Berlin%20are%20at%20number%206%2C%207%2C%208%20and%209.%20Montreal%20is%20at%20number%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faishe.gov.in%2Faishe%2FviewDocument.action%3Bjsessionid%3D9ACD95EC0083FAA240D97B7BFFFAA4B6%3FdocumentId%3D353%5C%22%3EAll%20India%20Survey%20on%20Higher%20Education%20(AISHE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20foreign%20students%20in%20Indian%20institutions%20was%20around%2046%2C000%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20these%20foreign%20students%20are%20from%20Nepal%2C%20followed%20by%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20three%20quarters%20of%20foreign%20students%20are%20enrolled%20in%20undergraduate%20courses%2C%20and%20the%20most%20popular%20subjects%20for%20this%20group%20are%20Technology%2C%20Business%20Administration%2C%20Science%20and%20Engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20has%20the%20world's%20second%20largest%20higher%20education%20system%20with%20over%2058%2C000%20higher%20education%20institutions.%20Nearly%202%2C400%20higher%20education%20institutions%20were%20added%20during%202021-22%2C%20as%20per%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718783340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-08%2Fstudent-generic_650x400_41470937092.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fqs-best-student-cities-2025-delhi-mumbai-among-top-150-cities-across-the-world-for-students-5922249%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Survey%20on%20Higher%20Education%20(AISHE)%20released%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20f