0gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20put%20us%20well%20on%20track%20to%20be%20a%20%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202050.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20I%20expect%20the%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20to%20have%20exceeded%20%2440%20trillion.%20What%20this%20effectively%20means%20is%20that%20over%20the%20next%2026%20years%2C%20India%20will%20potentially%20add%20%2436%20trillion%20to%20its%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20is%20over%20%245%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20other%20nation%20is%20remotely%20close%20to%20such%20a%20scale%20of%20possibility.%20There%20has%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20be%20Indian%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Adani%20Group%20Chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20infrastructure%20industry%20is%20undergoing%20a%20stunning%20change%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20which%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20appreciate%20fully%20when%20we%20look%20back%20a%20decade%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20kick-started%20an%20infrastructure%20capex%20cycle%20never%20seen%20before%2C%20and%20this%20lays%20the%20foundation%20for%20several%20decades%20of%20India's%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20starts%20with%20the%20quality%20of%20governance.%20Very%20few%20sectors%20globally%20are%20as%20tightly%20linked%20with%20government%20policy%20as%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gautam%20Adani.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publis