icient%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20the%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20tremendous%20rate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20India%20electric%20vehicle%20market%20size%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%20from%20USD%203.21%20billion%20in%202022%20to%20USD%20113.99%20billion%20in%202029%2C%20growing%20at%20a%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2066.52%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EFortune%20Business%20Insights.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJumping%20on%20the%20bandwagon%20are%20three%20young%20and%20innovative%20minds%20hailing%20from%20Kerala.%20Jacob%20Thekkekara%2C%20Azim%20Hashmi%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Hadi%20Mutheri%2C%20with%20their%20Kochi-based%20company%20Sugrah%20Mobility%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20have%20developed%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20solar-powered%20electric%20three-vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20while%20there%20were%20e-rickshaws%2C%20there%20were%20not%20any%20with%20a%20load-bearing%20capacity%20for%20transporting%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jacob%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Sugrah%20Mobility%20and%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20tricycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvailable%20for%20sale%20in%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F258975%2Findia-student-innovation-solar-electric-tricycle-smart-kisok-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tricycle%20is%20not%20just%20electric%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20100%20percent%20solar-run.%20He%20talks%20about%20the%20innovation%2C%20the%20idea%20behind%20it%2C%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%20in%20their%20plan%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20sustainable%20approach%20to%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESugrah%20is%20co-founder%20of%20Jacob%E2%80%99s%20second%20stint%20at%20business.%20While%20he%20founded%20another%20company%20on%20similar%20lines%20earlier%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20on%20doing%20something%20in%20his%20home%20state.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20along%20the%20same%20lines%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20which%20was%20more%20tangible%20and%20had%20a%20real%20impact.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20that%20startup%20and%20look%20for%20something%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudying%20markets%2C%20Jacob%20realised%20how%20the%20country%20depends%20a%20lot%20on%20three-wheelers%20for%20low%20to%20medium-scale%20transportation.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20odd%20%3Cem%3Ejugaads%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20many%20three-wheeler%20owners%20have%20done%20such%20as%20making%20it%20mechanical%20from%20a%20local%20mechanic.%20However%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20those%20can%20be%20dangerous%20and%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20such%20innovations%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20three-wheeler%20EVs%20with%20a%20good%20load-bearing%20capacity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20the%20potential%20of%20a%20product%20like%20that%20and%20decided%20to%20head%20in%20the%20same%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tricycle%20can%20be%20used%20for%20advertisement%20purposes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-16-1-1718105928-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352637%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20tricycle%20can%20be%20used%20for%20advertisement%20purposes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mechanical%20engineer%20with%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20from%20IIT-Madras%2C%20Jacob%20was%20joined%20by%20his%20engineer%20friends%2C%20Azim%20and%20Abdul%2C%20who%20had%20a%20similar%20vision.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20group%20started%20to%20brainstorm%20and%20research%20process.%20The%20company%20was%20founded%20the%20same%20year%2C%20whereas%20the%20tricycle%20was%20eventually%20launched%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETo%20bear%20the%20load%20of%20Indian%20transportation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20peddle-assisted%20three-wheeler%20can%20carry%20up%20to%20300%20kg%20of%20weight.%20Jacob%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20various%20features%2C%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20the%20only%20company%20that%20provides%20a%20working%20solar-powered%20three-wheeler%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%20For%20a%20solar-powered%20vehicle%20to%20run%20about%20100%20km%20a%20day%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20pedal-assisted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20runs%20entirely%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CFor%20an%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20we%20typically%20need%20to%20charge%20it%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20resulting%20in%20around%2019%20gm%20of%20CO2%20emissions%20per%20passenger%20per%20kilometre.%20However%2C%20by%20using%20solar%20power%20to%20generate%20electricity%2C%20this%20emis