0notes%20only%20after%20first%20reading.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20make%20notes%20majorly%20for%20Acts%20and%20rules.%20You%20can%20make%20notes%20by%20summarising%20the%20topic.%20Make%20sure%20that%20you%20do%20not%20end%20up%20writing%20another%20book.%20Final%20notes%20should%20be%2033%20percent%20of%20all%20topics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Know%20your%20DAF%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-fill-detailed-application-form-daf-ias-irs-ifs-officers-share-tips-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDetailed%20Application%20Form%20%3C%2Fa%3E(DAF)%20is%20very%20crucial%20for%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20need%20to%20fill%20out%20DAF%20which%20contains%20details%20like%20hometown%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20interests.%20Do%20not%20fill%20them%20recklessly%20as%20initial%20questions%20can%20be%20framed%20from%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterviews%20are%20very%20subjective.%20The%20first%20question%20asked%20in%20the%20interview%20determines%20the%20interview%20flow%20and%20whether%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20mould%20it%20in%20your%20favour.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20command%20of%20your%20DAF%2C%20then%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20sail%20through%20the%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20DAF%2C%20Aaditya%20mentioned%20listening%20to%20Ramcharitmanas%20(an%20epic%20poem%20that%20contains%20the%20deeds%20of%20Lord%20Rama)%20and%20watching%20Korean%20dramas%20as%20his%20interests.%20This%20framed%20his%20interview%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20similarities%20and%20differences%20between%20ancient%20values%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Indian%20and%20Korean%20societies.%20Another%20question%20was%20based